<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
    
    <ab xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:grantha maturity:83215">
        <lb n="1"/>svasti śrī
    </ab>
    <p>naṉ-maṅkalañ ciṟakka k<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>-v-irā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>-k<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>cari-pa<hi rend="grantha">nmar</hi>-āṉa <hi rend="grantha">tribhū</hi>vaṉa-c-<hi rend="grantha">cakrava<reg>r</reg>tti</hi>kaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-v<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice><hi rend="grantha">ra-rājentra-deva</hi>ṟku-t tiru-v-eḻutt’ iṭṭu-c cellā niṉṟa tiru-na
        
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>lli-yāṇṭu patt’ āvatu Aippi<choice><sic>c</sic><corr>k</corr></choice>ai-t tiṅkaḷil
        </p>
    
    <p>kuṟuppu-ṉāṭṭu vicaya-maṅkalattu-t tiru-m<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>ṟ-k<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>yil cittiram<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>ḻi-viṇṇakar' āḻvāṟku-t tiru-p-paṭimāṟṟukku Irupatt’ oṉpat’ accu e
        
    <lb n="3" break="no"/>m perumāṉ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> paṇṭārattu Oṭukka
    </p>
<p>
        I-vv-amutu-paṭi nittam ṉāṉāḻi-y-arici y-amutu-paṭi ceyvat' ā<supplied reason="omitted">ka</supplied> kal-veṭṭu vitt<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>ṉ
</p>
    <p>
    vicaiya-maṅkalattu veḷḷāḷaṉ cāttantaikaḷil ciṟiyāṉ t<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>vaṉ-āṉa
        
    <lb n="4"/>muṭi-koṇṭa-c<choice><orig>o</orig><reg>ō</reg></choice>ḻa mārāyaṉ<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>ṉ <hi rend="grantha">darmma</hi>ñ ca<hi rend="grantha">ntrādittya</hi>-varai celvat’ ākavum
        </p>
    <p>
        i-t-taṉmam Iṭaṅkai toṉṉūṟṟ’oṉpatu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">rakṣai</hi> I-<hi rend="grantha">dharmma</hi> Iṟa
        
    <lb n="5" break="no"/>kkuvāṉ vaḻi-vaḻi y-eḻ’ e-c-camaṟuvāṉ
    </p>
